title: [Gyldemar Forest, Crossroads]
description: As the old road ends, a barely visible path begins to the southeast.  The forest seems to be attempting to smother the path with new growth.  A few young saplings fight to survive among the large trees.

As the old road ends, a barely visible path begins to the southeast.  The forest seems to be attempting to smother the path with new growth.  A few young saplings fight to survive among the large trees.  Little moonlight filters through to the forest floor.
